2007-11-09  Akim Demaille  <demaille@gostai.com>

	Adjust locksystem macros.
	* urbi-lock-system.m4 (URBI_CHECK_LOCKSYSTEM_DEPENDENCIES)
	(URBI_CONFIGURE_LOCKSYSTEM, URBI_LOCKSYSTEM_CHECK_ADDR)
	(URBI_LOCKSYSTEM_COBF):
	Rename as...
	(_URBI_CHECK_LOCKSYSTEM_DEPENDENCIES)
        (_URBI_CONFIGURE_LOCKSYSTEM, _URBI_LOCKSYSTEM_CHECK_ADDR)
        (_URBI_LOCKSYSTEM_COBF):
	these, since they are private.
	Remove useless message about the default value (of course it you
	document --disable, it means it is enabled by default).
	(_URBI_CONFIGURE_LOCKSYSTEM): Define LOCKSYETEM_LIBS, not LIBS.

