	* ax_boost_regex.m4: Remove.
	* ax_boost_serialization.m4: Remove.
	* ax_boost_signals.m4: Remove.
	* ax_boost_test_exec_monitor.m4: Remove.
	* ax_boost_thread.m4: Remove.
	* ax_boost_unit_test_framework.m4: Remove.
	* ax_boost_wserialization.m4: Remove.
