2007-10-21  Benoit Sigoure  <tsuna@lrde.epita.fr>

	Don't use -pipe.
	* build-aux/urbi-prog-cxx.m4 (URBI_PROG_CXX): Do not use -pipe when
	GCC is detected, it doesn't speed up the compilation.  See this
	thread and its replies:
	  http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/automake/2007-10/msg00086.html

