2007-03-21  Akim Demaille  <akim.demaille@free.fr>

	Fix URBI_PROG_CXX
	Address https://core.gostai.com/projects/urbiengine-aibo/ticket/14
	* urbi-prog-cxx.m4: Don't set the language to C++ permanently
	as it confuses the rest of the script.  In particular, tests
	run by Libtools (e.g., findind dlfcn.h) were run in C++ context,
	although some bits of the set up were not complete (CXXCPP was
	not properly set).

