2007-01-30  Akim Demaille  <demaille@gostai.com>

	Upgrade check.mk to produce html
	* check.mk: here.

2007-01-30  Akim Demaille  <demaille@gostai.com>

	Make foo-ci more useful
	* svn-externals.mk (SVN): Defaults to svn-wrapper.sh, not svn.
	There is a nasty problem when we run "make libport-ci
	SVN=svn-wrapper.sh" for instance: in that case SVN is exported
	by make, and svn-wrapper.sh read the envvar SVN to look for the
	real SVN.  And there comes the endless loop of recursive svn-wrapper
	invocations.

